                </button>
                <div style="display: none; padding: 15px; background-color: #f9f9f9; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;">
                    <p>It’s also helpful to know the typical behaviors for each stage of a child’s development. Know what the normal stages of development are for preschool, elementary, middle school children and young teens. Learn the signs of sexual abuse. It will be easier to identify normal behaviors and behaviors that might be of concern. Don’t wait until it is too late to learn the signs of sexual abuse.</p>
